And it's a pretty cool
exercise because it

5
00:00:11,190 --> 00:00:12,900
has this little
virtual protractor

6
00:00:12,900 --> 00:00:15,910
that we can use to
actually measure angles.

7
00:00:15,909 --> 00:00:17,699
And I want to give
credit to the person who

8
